{"schema_version": "2.0", "product_id": "W07", "product_name": "Xiaomi Watch 2 Pro", "product_category": "smart_watch", "brand": "Xiaomi", "series": "Watch 2", "variant": "Pro", "source_region": "GLOBAL", "official_url": "https://www.mi.com/global/product/xiaomi-watch-2-pro/", "manual_url": null, "official_price": null, "currency": "AUD", "product_summary": "Xiaomi Watch 2 Pro 是搭载 Wear OS by Google 的高端智能手表，采用不锈钢机身，配备1.43英寸AMOLED圆形屏幕，分辨率466×466，最高亮度600nits。仅支持Android 8.0及以上且具备GMS的智能手机，不支持iOS和Android Go设备。支持蓝牙通话、Google Wallet NFC支付、5ATM防水、L1+L5双频五星GNSS定位、161种运动模式，以及心率、血氧、睡眠、压力、体成分和皮肤温度监测。BT版典型续航最长65小时，LTE版最长55小时；表体约54.5g（不含表带），尺寸约47.6×45.9×11.8mm（厚度不含心率传感器）。", "target_users": ["Android智能手机用户", "Wear OS应用需求用户", "商务与高端穿戴用户", "运动健身爱好者", "健康精细化监测需求用户", "LTE独立通信需求用户（LTE版本）"], "usage_scenarios": ["日常通勤佩戴", "商务会议使用", "运动健身记录", "全天健康监测", "Google Maps腕上导航", "Google Wallet银行卡支付", "泳池及近岸浅水活动", "LTE独立通话与联网（LTE版本）"], "wearable_specs": {"display_size_in": 1.43, "display_type": "AMOLED", "screen_resolution": "466×466", "max_brightness_nits": 600, "battery_life_typical_days": 2.7, "battery_life_heavy_days": 1, "charging_time_minutes": 45, "water_resistance": "5ATM", "positioning_type": "built_in_gnss", "bluetooth_call": true, "nfc_support": true, "heart_rate_monitoring": true, "blood_oxygen_monitoring": true, "sleep_monitoring": true, "stress_monitoring": true, "sports_modes_count": 161, "sports_features": ["L1+L5双频GPS、Galileo、GLONASS、BeiDou、QZSS五星GNSS定位", "161种运动模式", "泳池及近岸浅水运动记录", "体成分测量", "皮肤温度监测", "支持Mi Fitness、Strava与Suunto运动数据生态"], "system_compatibility": "仅支持Android 8.0及以上且具备GMS 21.30.12及以上的智能手机；不支持iOS和Android Go设备", "weight_g": 54.5, "dimensions_mm": "47.6×45.9×11.8", "strap_material": "氟橡胶或真皮（不同配色版本标配）"}, "source_records": [{"field_scope": ["basic_info", "product_summary", "target_users", "usage_scenarios", "wearable_specs.sports_modes_count", "wearable_specs.sports_features", "wearable_specs.nfc_support"], "source_url": "https://www.mi.com/global/product/xiaomi-watch-2-pro/", "source_type": "product_page", "source_region": "GLOBAL", "accessed_at": "2026-07-21"}, {"field_scope": ["wearable_specs.display_size_in", "wearable_specs.display_type", "wearable_specs.screen_resolution", "wearable_specs.max_brightness_nits", "wearable_specs.battery_life_typical_days", "wearable_specs.charging_time_minutes", "wearable_specs.water_resistance", "wearable_specs.positioning_type", "wearable_specs.system_compatibility", "wearable_specs.weight_g", "wearable_specs.dimensions_mm", "wearable_specs.strap_material"], "source_url": "https://www.mi.com/global/product/xiaomi-watch-2-pro/specs/", "source_type": "specs_page", "source_region": "GLOBAL", "accessed_at": "2026-07-21"}, {"field_scope": ["wearable_specs.battery_life_heavy_days", "wearable_specs.charging_time_minutes", "wearable_specs.system_compatibility", "wearable_specs.water_resistance"], "source_url": "https://www.mi.com/global/support/faq/details/KA-42562/", "source_type": "support_page", "source_region": "GLOBAL", "accessed_at": "2026-07-21"}, {"field_scope": ["usage_scenarios", "product_summary"], "source_url": "https://www.mi.com/global/support/faq/details/KA-515587/", "source_type": "support_page", "source_region": "GLOBAL", "accessed_at": "2026-07-21"}], "data_quality": {"collector": "王梓璁", "reviewer": "张静雯", "status": "approved", "notes": "1.Xiaomi Watch 2 Pro存在BT版和LTE版，当前文件统一描述该产品系列；2.官方规格页标注屏幕最高亮度600nits，原1500nits属于其他型号参数；3.BT版典型续航最长65小时，换算约2.7天；LTE版最长55小时，约2.3天；battery_life_typical_days按续航更长的BT版上限2.7记录；4.官方FAQ标注重度使用约24小时，battery_life_heavy_days填写1；5.规格页标注充电约45分钟，FAQ另有约1小时表述；charging_time_minutes优先采用规格页的45分钟，并记录为约值；6.仅支持Android 8.0及以上且具备指定GMS版本的手机，不支持iOS和Android Go；7.产品页对比表给出161种运动模式，因此sports_modes_count填写161；8.NFC主要用于Google Wallet银行卡支付，可用性受国家、地区、银行和卡组织支持情况影响；9.LTE版支持eSIM独立通话和联网，BT版不支持eSIM，且具体功能取决于运营商；10.表体重量约54.5g，不含表带；厚度不含心率传感器；11.银色版本标配棕色真皮表带，黑色版本标配黑色氟橡胶表带；12.官方页面未标注蓝宝石玻璃、钛金属钢带、运动vlog、心率广播、跌倒检测等内容，故不保留；13.原manual_url无法作为可验证的GLOBAL官方说明书直链，故填写null。"}, "data_updated_at": "2026-07-22"}
